==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ripper
<hw>Rip"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, rips; a ripping tool.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A tool for trimming the edges of roofing
slates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Anything huge, extreme, startling, etc.</def>
<mark>[Slang.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ripper bill</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Ripper act</ent>⟦br⟧
